            "text": "Fig. 1: Simulation CT with two suspicious areas of opacity: right lung apex (left) and left lung inferior lobe (right)",
            "type": "figure"
        },
        "FIGREF1": {
            "text": "Fig. 2: First CBCT: only the suspicious left inferior lobe opacity is encompassed in the field of view",
            "type": "figure"
        }
